text.section: Any person who violates any of the provisions of KRS 359.020 or 359.030 shall be guilty of a Class D felony.
Any person who violates any of the provisions of subsection (1) of KRS 359.050 shall be guilty of a violation.
Any person who violates any of the provisions of subsection (2) of KRS 359.090 shall be guilty of a Class A misdemeanor.

law.history: Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 463, sec. 40, effective July 14, 1992. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 4775, 4784, 4796.
